{
  "version": "2",
  "flowTitle": "Document Extraction & Spreadsheet Generator",
  "trigger": {
    "valid": true,
    "type": "WEBHOOK",
    "settings": {
      "input": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "documentUrl": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Input for documentUrl"
          },
          "userAnswers": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Input for userAnswers"
          },
          "documentType": {
            "type": "string",
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "const": "file",
                "title": "File (PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, CSV)"
              },
              {
                "const": "webpage",
                "title": "Webpage / Website"
              },
              {
                "const": "youtube",
                "title": "YouTube Video"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "additionalProperties": false
      }
    }
  },
  "actions": [
    {
      "name": "8153209c-ec36-4ede-b8ee-a1b3e2479c2f",
      "valid": true,
      "displayName": "Route by Document Type",
      "type": "BRANCH",
      "settings": {},
      "paths": [
        {
          "name": "079cf446-9ae4-4856-8d19-3283444ff72d",
          "valid": true,
          "displayName": "File (PDF / DOCX / XLSX / CSV)",
          "type": "BRANCH_PATH",
          "settings": {
            "ruleset": {
              "type": "CUSTOM",
              "input": {
                "type": "or",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "type": "and",
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "condition": "text_matches",
                        "id": "c8c75b4d-3245-4c9b-b750-db53b90833cb",
                        "data": "{{ trigger[\"body\"][\"documentType\"] }}",
                        "comparator": "file"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "actions": [
            {
              "name": "b0d32001-021b-4b31-993e-2ff9b25572d7",
              "valid": true,
              "displayName": "Extract Text from Document File",
              "type": "PIECE",
              "settings": {
                "pieceName": "@taskade/automade-internalpiece-media",
                "pieceVersion": "1.0.0",
                "actionName": "pdf.convertToText",
                "input": {
                  "pdfUrl": "{{ trigger[\"body\"][\"documentUrl\"] }}"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "4fb32826-d68c-46a5-8cbf-3a4c99ed3aa0",
          "valid": true,
          "displayName": "Webpage or YouTube (fallback)",
          "type": "BRANCH_PATH",
          "settings": {
            "ruleset": {
              "type": "FALLBACK"
            }
          },
          "actions": [
            {
              "name": "920ddc5d-ba73-4443-a588-686612131700",
              "valid": true,
              "displayName": "Scrape Webpage / Extract URL Content",
              "type": "PIECE",
              "settings": {
                "pieceName": "@taskade/automade-internalpiece-media",
                "pieceVersion": "1.0.0",
                "actionName": "website.extract",
                "input": {
                  "websiteUrl": "{{ trigger[\"body\"][\"documentUrl\"] }}",
                  "errorBehavior": "continue"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3276cbbb-6b30-4248-8189-7ca84f545de2",
      "valid": true,
      "displayName": "AI: Generate Spreadsheet from Extracted Content",
      "type": "PIECE",
      "settings": {
        "pieceName": "@taskade/automade-internalpiece-openai",
        "pieceVersion": "1.0.0",
        "actionName": "ai.ask",
        "input": {
          "input": "{{ b0d32001-021b-4b31-993e-2ff9b25572d7[\"content\"] }}{{ 920ddc5d-ba73-4443-a588-686612131700[\"content\"] }}",
          "model": "openai/gpt-5.4",
          "prompt": "You are an expert data analyst. You have been given extracted text content from a document (PDF, Word, webpage, spreadsheet, or similar). Your job is to transform this content into a well-structured spreadsheet.\n\nUser Preferences: {{ trigger[\"body\"][\"userAnswers\"] }}\nSource URL: {{ trigger[\"body\"][\"documentUrl\"] }}\n\nInstructions:\n1. Deeply read and understand the document content\n2. Identify all data tables, lists, key-value pairs, and structured information\n3. Create a meaningful multi-sheet spreadsheet that captures ALL the important data\n4. Synthesize and normalize the data — do not just copy it verbatim\n5. Add calculated columns where useful (totals, status labels, priority scores)\n6. If the document mentions names, dates, values, companies — USE them in the rows\n7. Generate at least 2-3 sheets. Always include a Summary sheet with key insights\n8. Column names must be specific (e.g. 'Contract Value ($)' not 'Value')\n\nRespond with ONLY valid JSON — no markdown, no explanation:\n{\n  \"title\": \"Document-derived Title — Structured Spreadsheet\",\n  \"dataType\": \"financial|project_tasks|meeting_notes|sales_data|inventory|report|other\",\n  \"summary\": \"What was extracted and the key insights found in this document\",\n  \"sheets\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Sheet Name\",\n      \"description\": \"What this sheet captures from the document\",\n      \"columns\": [\"Column A\", \"Column B\", \"Column C\"],\n      \"rows\": [\n        [\"val1\", \"val2\", \"val3\"]\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "type": "http_response",
      "body": {
        "type": "json",
        "data": {
          "type": "basic",
          "payload": [
            {
              "result": "{{ 3276cbbb-6b30-4248-8189-7ca84f545de2[\"result\"] }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "key": "trigger"
    }
  ]
}